â”œâ”€â”€ server.c         # Server-side code (handles multiple clients)
â”œâ”€â”€ forum.c          # Forum data logic (topic + post handling)
â”œâ”€â”€ forum.h          # Forum data structure definitions
â”œâ”€â”€ forum.txt        # Forum storage (created at runtime)
â”œâ”€â”€ Makefile         # (Optional) Build automation
â””â”€â”€ README.txt       # Project documentation

